data.name: Macquarie Car Loan
data.description: With our loan options you can choose either a variable or fixed rate to suit your needs.

features.additionalInfo: You can access and manage your car loan account details online anytime, anywhere​. Manage upcoming payments, request documents and update your details.
Repayments are to be made by Direct Debit.
You may make additional payments or repay your loan in full at any time.

constraints.additionalInfo: Minimum limit for Macquarie refinance is $5,000, subject to credit assessment.

eligibility.additionalInfo: Loan applications, refinances and balloon amounts are subject to credit assessment.

fees.name: Establishment Fee
fees.additionalInfo: Debited to your Account on the Settlement Date. Fee charged is based on origination channel.

fees.name: Discharge Fee
fees.additionalInfo: Payable when your loan is discharged, including if you repay your loan early.

fees.name: Break Cost
fees.additionalInfo: Payable if the whole of your fixed rate loan is repaid early (including if you elect to repay the Total Amount Owing early, or the Total Amount Owing otherwise becomes due and payable in full before the date the final repayment is due).

fees.name: Account Keeping Fee
fees.additionalInfo: Payable monthly for all car loans.
